data.description: A beautiful fully upgraded 3 bedroom and 1 bathroom home with Laminated Wood Floorings throughout, dual paned windows, open and spacious kitchen. dining area, living room with inside laundry, recessed lightings, patio at back with a very low maintenance back yard. Updated electrical and plumbing systems throughout the home with Central AC (split system) and Heat. Possibility of existing newer Refrigerator, Stove, Washer and Dryer included with home! Must see to appreciate!
